# Python Execution

Always prefix Python commands with `uv run` instead of calling `python` directly.

```bash
# ❌ BAD
python script.py
python -m dagnabbit.scripts.train_encoder
python -c "import torch; print(torch.__version__)"

# ✅ GOOD
uv run python script.py
uv run python -m dagnabbit.scripts.train_encoder
uv run python -c "import torch; print(torch.__version__)"
```
